{"tid":2221326,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★新移民對香港減慢人口老化發揮積極效用","createTime":"2020-09-28T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T11:51:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"66cfac6559330dac8f28cc686ad6a8cbfcc8efce","tid":2221326,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"若缺乏內地來港新移民，香港經濟的創業能力也許更加不濟。不過這並非說新移民在創業精神上勝過本地人，畢竟他們教育程度一般較低，而且對本地經濟環境不夠熟悉；此說無非指出，<span class=\"xx-large\">他們對減慢人口老化趨勢發揮積極效用</span>。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n除了創業精神，新移民對在職人口的確注入一支強心針，最少佔本港整體工作人口五份之一至四份之一。新移民雖然教育程度相對較低，但勝在年輕力壯且勤力，兩者均為有利條件。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n純粹針對新移民坐享公共資源，而忽略他們對香港經濟所作的重大貢獻，未免一葉障目，以偏概全。<br />\n<a href=\"http://wangyujian.hku.hk/?p=10338&amp;lang=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwangyujian.hku.hk%2F%3Fp%3D10338%26lang%3Dzh-hant&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hISiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=6e208056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wangyujian.hku.hk/?p=10338&amp;lang=zh-hant</a>"},{"pid":"ce194bc938f910ccfdfb20a848de225fe2c5b01a","tid":2221326,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auqMieR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauqMieR.gif&h=045312c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9686856058b4506ae209017abdd717e13b46381","tid":2221326,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"老貓中出過啲大陸雞幾多次"},{"pid":"e6c29d6b0cd0da8dc59e6279641e6c841eed8bfe","tid":2221326,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23K1RzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23K1RzA.png&h=4d66e751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5rfV1g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5rfV1g.png&h=04d94489&s